Version 1.0 of Loki Scanner Application, it was created by Baha' Mahmoud & Mahmoud Shahin March 2022.
this application depends on 3 addons, 2 of them are Custom Visualization
	1) TA_Loki
	2) Splunk Sankey Diagram - Custom Visualization ### https://splunkbase.splunk.com/app/3112/
	3) Force Directed App For Splunk ## https://splunkbase.splunk.com/app/3767/
	 
only one setup is required, set the MACRO of loki_index to a specific index
Enjoy using and add more ideas to it.
Happy Splunking ^^